# ========================================
# Usage Instructions
# ========================================
# npm run dev              → Uses this .env.local (mock mode)
# npm run dev:mock         → Explicitly uses mock mode
# npm run dev:auth         → Override to production mode (real Supabase)
# npm run dev:integration  → Same as dev:auth
# npm run build            → Production build
#
# To switch modes: Change VITE_APP_MODE above
# To test auth: Set VITE_APP_MODE=production or use npm run dev:auth
#
